description: Alecci's Ice Delights is serving up the finest frozen treats you could ask for! Shaved ice is the perfect treat when you're out and about on the streets of Ohio, and their homemade Italian Ice is another classic favorite for your sweet tooth. Whichever delicious option you choose, Alecci's Ice Delights is sure to put a smile on your face, so keep an eye out for them today!
name: Alecci's Ice Delights
